    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/2867fab1ad931edf93c3f5d0e3371394.poster.avif?t=1755871815\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/2867fab1ad931edf93c3f5d0e3371394.webm?t=1755871815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/2867fab1ad931edf93c3f5d0e3371394.mp4?t=1755871815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Soulers》是一款可以减缓时间并组建多样化队伍进行战斗的射击游戏。 作为联合舰的船长“马奇纳”，击败强大的Boss，将他们招募为队员，克服危机，并揭开这个世界隐藏的真相！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/df6c140f0805840e8758838102dea203.poster.avif?t=1755871815\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/df6c140f0805840e8758838102dea203.webm?t=1755871815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/df6c140f0805840e8758838102dea203.mp4?t=1755871815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>减缓时间的力量</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >马奇纳拥有减缓时间的特殊能力。躲避敌人的攻击，反击飞来的导弹，扭转战局！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/38f6488fc77a397ce2309e7edfa2540e.poster.avif?t=1755871815\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/38f6488fc77a397ce2309e7edfa2540e.webm?t=1755871815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/38f6488fc77a397ce2309e7edfa2540e.mp4?t=1755871815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>招募队员并组建你的团队</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邂逅拥有独特能力的Soulers，并将他们招募为队员。定制你的团队，打造属于你的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/3e9f51e42555b876bb14e628ba435e1c.poster.avif?t=1755871815\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/3e9f51e42555b876bb14e628ba435e1c.webm?t=1755871815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/3e9f51e42555b876bb14e628ba435e1c.mp4?t=1755871815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级和自定义</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成任务并获得升级。强化你的角色、武器和队员，迎接更艰难的战斗挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/9cd77d54876ae24cccdb2116ded0427d.poster.avif?t=1755871815\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/9cd77d54876ae24cccdb2116ded0427d.webm?t=1755871815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388920/extras/9cd77d54876ae24cccdb2116ded0427d.mp4?t=1755871815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
